                    <li>If account is not paid within 7 days the credits details supplied.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4">
                <h3>Signature</h3>
                <div class="text-4xl italic text-indigo-500">G-shoppers</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full h-0.5 bg-indigo-500"></div>

        <div class="p-4">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center">Thank you very much for shopping with us.
            </div>
            
        </div>

